# AlMarket – Backend API

AlMarket Backend is the backend service powering the AlMarket online game item store. It handles orders, payments, order tracking, admin tools, and live chat between admin and users.

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

- **Node.js** + **Express.js**
- **MongoDB** (via Mongoose)
- **Stripe API** (secure payments)
- **Socket.IO** (real-time per-order chat)
- **dotenv**, **CORS**, **body-parser**, etc.
- **Hosted on** Render or Railway

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Create orders with in-game ID and UC package
- 💳 Stripe-based secure payment (no card data stored)
- 🕒 Auto status updates:
  - `Ýatyryldy` – if not paid
  - `Garasylyar` – after Stripe payment
  - `Gowşuryldy` – set manually by admin
- 💬 Admin ↔ User one-on-one chat (per order)
- 📋 Admin panel support (status control, logs)
- 🔢 Point system support (e.g. 60UC = 5 points)
- 🔄 UC splitting logic (e.g. 600 = 300+300)
- 🌐 Multi-language support from frontend

---

## 🔐 .env Configuration

Create a `.env` file in root:

```env
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_url
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=your_stripe_secret_key
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_stripe_webhook_secret
CLIENT_URL=https://al-market.vercel.app
